<body id="page-top">
  <%- include ('layout/header') -%>
    <div class="container">
      <form action="/user/save_about_me" method="post">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="w100">
            <div class="col-sm-12 ">
                <div class="lDiv w45">
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="cover_photo">Template<span class="mandatorySymbol">*</span></label>
                    <select name="template" id="template_name" class="form-control" required>
                      <option selected>Choose Template</option>
                      <option value="1">One</option>
                      <option value="2">Two</option>
                      <option value="3">Three</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="rDiv w45">
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="profile_pic">Industry<span class="mandatorySymbol">*</span></label>
                  <select name="industry" id="industry_name" class="form-control" required>
                    <option selected>Select Industry</option>
                    <option value="1">One</option>
                    <option value="2">Two</option>
                    <option value="3">Three</option>
                  </select>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>


        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="company_name">Description<span class="mandatorySymbol">*</span></label>
          <textarea name="editor1" required>  <p><b>We are a team of professional Insurance and Financial Advisor who are here to cater to your needs and advice related to Life/Health Insurance plans and Mutrual Fund Investments. </b></p> <p><b>We have been offering Insurance and Financial advice to our customers for last 13 years.Our expertise ranges from individual & family insurances to a broad range of business insurance,financial products(Mutual Funds) and advice.</b></p>
          <p><b>We have a proven track record in managing risk and building certainty.We also provide support to people who wish to make a career in Insurance and Financial Sector.</b></p>
          <p><b>Our Achievements :-</b></p>
          <p><b>3 times MDRT(USA),2016,2012017,2019</b></p>
          <p><b>Corporate club Member - Past 5 year</b></p>
          <p><b>Experience :-</b></p>
          <p><b>More than 20 yrs in Financial Services Industry</b></p>
           <p><b>Assets Under Management:-</b></p>
          <p><b>80 Cr</b></p>
          <p><b>Risk Under Management :-</b></p>
          <p><b>250 Cr , 300 Lives</b></p>
          <p><b>No of Family being Served :-</b></p>
          <p><b>20 UHNI</b></p>
          <p><b>50 HNI</b></p></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn saveBtn">SAVE</button>
        <button type="reset" class="btn resetBtn"><i class="fa fa-undo" aria-hidden="true"></i> Reset</button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <%- include ('layout/footer') -%>
      <%- include ('../layout/js') -%>
        <script src="https://cdn.ckeditor.com/4.16.1/standard/ckeditor.js"></script>
